1119. To GEORGE SPALATINUS.

Epistolae acl diuersos p. 523. Louvain. HN: Lond. xiii. 40: LB. 512. 6 July 1520.

[As the Imperial Election is over (l. 8)⁷ only 1519, 1520, 1521 are possible. For various reasons 1519 is unlikely: in 1521 at this time the breach between Hutten (l. 33) and Erasmus had begun. 1520 is corroborated by Erasmus' pro- jected return to Germany (ll. 22—3) and by the letter to Melanchthon (1. 26).]
